67class PropertyMeta
68{
69private:
70 std::string name;
71 PropertyType type;
72 PropertyValue min, def, max;
73 OnChangeCallback on_change;
74
75public:
76 PropertyType get_type() const;
77 PropertyValue get_min() const;
78 PropertyValue get_def() const;
79 PropertyValue get_max() const;
80 std::string get_name() const;
81
82 void changed(std::any argument) const;
83
84 template<class T> PropertyMeta(std::string _name, PropertyType _type, T _min, T _def, T _max,
85 OnChangeCallback _on_change = nullptr) :
86 name(_name), type(_type), min(_min), def(_def), max(_max), on_change(_on_change) {}
87 template<class T> PropertyMeta(std::string _name, PropertyType _type, T _def,
88 OnChangeCallback _on_change = nullptr) :
89 name(_name), type(_type), def(_def), on_change(_on_change) {}
90
91 PropertyMeta(const PropertyMeta&) = delete;
92};

244template<typename PropertyMetaT>
245size_t Property<PropertyMetaT>::get_size() const
246{
247 switch(get_type())
248 {
249 case PropertyType::Int:
250 return sizeof(int);
251 case PropertyType::Float:
252 return sizeof(float);
253 case PropertyType::Color:
254 return sizeof(bvec);
255 case PropertyType::IntVec:
256 return sizeof(ivec);
257 case PropertyType::FloatVec:
258 return sizeof(vec);
259 case PropertyType::String:
260 return get_string().size();
261 default:
262 return 0;
263 }
264}

266template<typename PropertyMetaT>
267std::string Property<PropertyMetaT>::to_string() const
268{
269 switch(get_type())
270 {
271 case PropertyType::Int:
272 return std::to_string(get_int());
273
274 case PropertyType::Float:
275 return std::to_string(get_float());
276
277 case PropertyType::Color:
278 return std::to_string(get_color().r) + " " + std::to_string(get_color().g) + " " + std::to_string(get_color().b);
279
280 case PropertyType::IntVec:
281 return std::to_string(get_ivec().x) + " " + std::to_string(get_ivec().y) + " " + std::to_string(get_ivec().z);
282
283 case PropertyType::FloatVec:
284 return std::to_string(get_fvec().x) + " " + std::to_string(get_fvec().y) + " " + std::to_string(get_fvec().z);
285
286 case PropertyType::String:
287 return get_string();
288
289 default:
290 return "";
291 }

294template<typename PropertyMetaT>
295bool Property<PropertyMetaT>::set_check_type(PropertyType type) const
296{
297 static constexpr std::string_view typenames[] =
298 {
299 "int", "float", "color", "int vector", "float vector", "string"
300 };
301
302 if(get_type() != type)
303 {
304 // conoutf("Error: %s, incorrect property assignment type: got %s, expected %s",
305 // meta.get_name().c_str(), std::string(typenames[static_cast<size_t>(type)]).c_str(),
306 // std::string(typenames[static_cast<size_t>(get_type())]).c_str());
307
308 return false;
309 }
310
311 return true;
312}

358template<typename PropertyMetaT>
359void Property<PropertyMetaT>::set_clamped(PropertyValue value)
360{
361 switch(get_type())
362 {
363 case PropertyType::Int:
364 {
365 int v = std::get<int>(value);
366 this->value = std::clamp(v, std::get<int>(meta.get_min()), std::get<int>(meta.get_max()));
367 break;
368 }
369
370 case PropertyType::Float:
371 {
372 float v = std::get<float>(value);
373 this->value = std::clamp(v, std::get<float>(meta.get_min()), std::get<float>(meta.get_max()));
374 break;
375 }
376
377 case PropertyType::IntVec:
378 {
379 ivec v = std::get<ivec>(value);
380 this->value = ivec(v).min(std::get<ivec>(meta.get_max()))
381 .max(std::get<ivec>(meta.get_min()));
382 break;
383 }
384
385 case PropertyType::FloatVec:
386 {
387 vec v = std::get<vec>(value);
388 this->value = vec(v).min(std::get<vec>(meta.get_max()))
389 .max(std::get<vec>(meta.get_min()));
390 break;
391 }
392
393 default:
394 this->value = value;
395 break;
396 }
397}

448static void _prop_cmd_result_value(PropertyValue value, PropertyType type)
449{
450 switch(type)
451 {
452 case PropertyType::Int:
453 intret(std::get<int>(value));
454 break;
455
456 case PropertyType::Float:
457 floatret(std::get<float>(value));
458 break;
459
460 case PropertyType::Color:
461 intret(std::get<bvec>(value).tohexcolor());
462 break;
463
464 case PropertyType::IntVec:
465 {
466 const ivec& v = std::get<ivec>(value);
467 result(tempformatstring("%d %d %d", v.x, v.y, v.z));
468 break;
469 }
470
471 case PropertyType::FloatVec:
472 {
473 const vec& v = std::get<vec>(value);
474 result(tempformatstring("%f %f %f", v.x, v.y, v.z));
475 break;
476 }
477
478 case PropertyType::String:
479 result(std::get<std::string>(value).c_str());
480 break;
481
482 default: break;
483 }
484}

536template<typename PropertyMetaT>
537void Property<PropertyMetaT>::pack(std::vector<uint8_t>& buf) const
538{
539 size_t data_size = get_size();
540
541 vectorput(buf, data_size);
542
543 switch(get_type())
544 {
545 case PropertyType::Int:
546 {
547 vectorput(buf, get_int());
548 break;
549 }
550
551 case PropertyType::Float:
552 {
553 vectorput(buf, get_float());
554 break;
555 }
556
557 case PropertyType::Color:
558 {
559 vectorput(buf, get_color());
560 break;
561 }
562
563 case PropertyType::IntVec:
564 {
565 vectorput(buf, get_ivec());
566 break;
567 }
568
569 case PropertyType::FloatVec:
570 {
571 vectorput(buf, get_fvec());
572 break;
573 }
574
575 case PropertyType::String:
576 {
577 std::string data = get_string();
578 // Null-terminator not needed, since we know the size
579 vectorput(buf, reinterpret_cast<const uint8_t*>(data.data()), data.size());
580 break;
581 }
582
583 default: break;
584 }

596template<typename PropertyMetaT>
597size_t Property<PropertyMetaT>::unpack(const uint8_t* buf, size_t buf_size)
598{
599 size_t buf_read = 0;
600 const size_t* data_size_packed = nullptr;
601
602 if(buf_size <= sizeof(*data_size_packed))
603 {
604 // conoutf("Error unpacking prop '%s': not enough data to get the size!", meta.get_name().c_str());
605 return 0;
606 }
607
608 data_size_packed = reinterpret_cast<const size_t*>(buf);
609
610 buf_read += sizeof(*data_size_packed);
611
612 static auto size_check = [&](size_t needed_size)
613 {
614 if(buf_size - buf_read < needed_size)
615 {
616 // conoutf("Error unpacking prop '%s': not enough data!", meta.get_name().c_str());
617 return false;
618 }
619
620 return true;
621 };
622
623 switch(get_type())
624 {
625 case PropertyType::Int:
626 case PropertyType::Color:
627 case PropertyType::Float:
628 if(*data_size_packed != get_size())
629 {
630 // conoutf("Error unpacking prop '%s': unexpected data size! Wanted: %lu, got: %lu",
631 // meta.get_name().c_str(), get_size(), *data_size_packed);
632
633 return 0;
634 }
635 break;
636
637 default: break;
638 }
639
640 switch(get_type())
641 {
642 case PropertyType::Int:
643 {
644 if(!size_check(get_size()))
645 {
646 return 0;
647 }
648
649 int ival;
650 memcpy(&ival, buf + buf_read, get_size());
651 buf_read += get_size();
652 value = ival;
653 break;
654 }
655
656 case PropertyType::Float:
657 {
658 if(!size_check(get_size()))
659 {
660 return 0;
661 }
662
663 float fval;
664 memcpy(&fval, buf + buf_read, get_size());
665 buf_read += get_size();
666 value = fval;
667 break;
668 }
669
670 case PropertyType::Color:
671 {
672 if(!size_check(get_size()))
673 {
674 return 0;
675 }
676
677 bvec cval;
678 memcpy(&cval, buf + buf_read, get_size());
679 buf_read += get_size();
680 value = cval;
681 break;
682 }
683
684 case PropertyType::IntVec:
685 {
686 if(!size_check(get_size()))
687 {
688 return 0;
689 }
690
691 ivec ivecval;
692 memcpy(&ivecval, buf + buf_read, get_size());
693 buf_read += get_size();
694 value = ivecval;
695 break;
696 }
697
698 case PropertyType::FloatVec:
699 {
700 if(!size_check(get_size()))
701 {
702 return 0;
703 }
704
705 vec vecval;
706 memcpy(&vecval, buf + buf_read, get_size());
707 buf_read += get_size();
708 value = vecval;
709 break;
710 }
711
712 case PropertyType::String:
713 {
714 if(!size_check(*data_size_packed))
715 {
716 return 0;
717 }
718
719 std::string sval(reinterpret_cast<const char*>(buf + buf_read), *data_size_packed);
720 buf_read += *data_size_packed;
721 value = sval;
722 break;
723 }
724
725 default: break;
726 }
727
728 return buf_read;
729}

866template<typename PropertyT, std::size_t N>
867bool set_prop(std::string name, PropertyValue value, std::array<PropertyT, N>& props,
868 std::any on_change_arg = std::any())
869{
870 PropertyT* prop = find_prop(name, props);
871 if(!prop)
872 {
873 // conoutf("Property %s not found!", name.c_str());
874 return false;
875 }
876
877 prop->set(value, on_change_arg);
878 return true;

913void pack_props(const std::array<PropertyT, N>& props, std::vector<uint8_t>& buf)

930template<typename PropertyT, std::size_t N>
931size_t unpack_props(const std::vector<uint8_t>& buf, std::array<PropertyT, N>& props)
932{
933 size_t prop_idx = 0;
934 size_t read_pos = 0;
935
936 while(read_pos < buf.size())
937 {
938 if(prop_idx >= N)
939 {
940 break;
941 }
942
943 PropertyT &prop = props[prop_idx];
944
945 int unpacked_size = prop.unpack(buf.data() + read_pos, buf.size() - read_pos);
946 if(!unpacked_size)
947 {
948 break;
949 }
950
951 read_pos += unpacked_size;
952 prop_idx++;
953 }
954
955 return prop_idx;
956}
